texts.text: >A single demon gazes upon the world.
>A world festering anger and hate. A world rife with conflict and strife.
>A strange world where its denizens bury their deepest fears.
Man, cram school's such a drag.
I know, right? Wanna ditch?
What would you like to have today?

Hmm... Curry!
I want curry!
Thanks for coming out today, everyone!

*Roar*
Shionyan!!
Now, let's go over what went wrong today...
Observing the world again, brother?
>Chi You turns around after hearing his brother's voice.
>And sees 81 of his brothers all gathered together.
My brothers, what brings you all here today?

Please, listen.
It's terrible.

This world is all wrong!
No place can be this peaceful!
Humans and demons should be in constant conflict with one another!
And yet, they are all simply lazing about and doing nothing!
What is it that you are trying to tell me...?

Do you not understand?
Once more, brother...!
We must plunge this world into a state of war once more!
We fell to Huang Di last time, but this time will be different!
There is no way we can lose to these sloths!
We shall reign victorious and plunge this world into a state of war!
And we need you to lead our armies, brother!
You will, will you not?
I see. So that is what you wished to tell me...
But I will not engage in such conflict...
W-Why not?!
Please do not tell me that you have become like them, brother?!

I see...
Fine, so be it!
All of you, he has spoken! He will not be participating in this conflict!
But if he is not willing to lead us, who will?!
Whoever that may be will need to be strong and powerful!
No, they must appear to be a true leader if they are to start a war.
Wits! Wits and tact are what is needed to achieve victory!
Power, leadership and wits... In that case, how about this?!
We will all fight for this honor!
We shall use our power to subjugate demons and use our wits to vanquish our enemies!
And the last one standing shall be our new leader!
So war it is...!
Let us compare not just our own abilities, but our potential as leaders!
Brothers, let us take this opportunity to choose our new leader!

Excellent...
Now, we must muster our forces!
Once our individual armies are ready, we shall begin!
*Roar*
They must be planning something since they have gathered en masse as such...
Do they intend to bring war upon this peaceful world?
Who goes there? Show yourself.
>Chi You stares into the darkness and sees a lone demon emerge from it.
Chi You, it has been quite a while.
Huang Di, my archenemy...
To think that you would come and see what my brothers are doing yourself.
You saw them, did you not? They have already left for the humans' world.
If you wish to stop them, now is the time.
Indeed I plan to. However, I must discuss a matter with you first.
With me?
You are the eldest of the Chi You brothers. You are the most renowned.
The one whose rage burned like fire, the one whose veins ran with ice water,
the one who loved to fight above all else.
So why is it that you wish to recuse yourself from this conflict?
If you were to join them, you would surely stand above them as their leader,
and started this conflict all on your own.
Huang Di, my archenemy, you deserve to know the truth...
I still do not understand why I lost our last battle.
My brothers said so themselves.
There is no way that we could lose to these slothful humans.
But I sought conflict and lost to the very same thing.
I sought power while you sought peace. And I ultimately fell to that.
It is as if common logic does not apply in this situation...!
Your mind still dwells on that loss...?
Chi You, my archenemy, allow me to give you just one piece of advice.
If you wish to know why you lost that day,
try stopping your brothers and this senseless war.
Stop them? You expect a god of war to do such a thing?
Yes, because the answer you seek lay beyond that.
If you say so. I shall see for myself...
However, if I do not find the answer I seek, I will raise my own army and start a new war.
Be prepared for when that time comes.
Let us hope that it does not come to that...
>You venture through thick fog as you head towards the Hideout,
>and you suddenly bump into someone.

E-Excuse me...
Oh, [sys user_name], it's you.
Are you hurt?
Talk about a surprise!
I'm okay.
Likewise. I was just about to pull my airsoft gun on you too.
Are you on your way to the Hideout? If so, we can go together.

But still...
The fog's been so thick lately.
It's hard to even see where we're walking, so let's take it slow.
Now, shall we?

Hello.
Hm...?
*Groan*
Oh, hey, Rika, [sys user_name].
Hello, Ririn. Did something happen to Gakuto? He doesn't seem well.
Oh, uh... Well...
Shionyan's show got cancelled...!
What?!

Not just today's show.
Everything for a while too.
How am I supposed to get my daily dose of Shionyan now...?!
Daily dose of Shionyan?
Normal people don't need that, but I'm guessing this thing does.
Yeah, I didn't know that's what piggy needs to live. It's so new to me!
But why is Shiori being suspended from being an idol? What happened...?
I'm still an idol.

Oh, Shiori!
There you are.
I was taking a call just now. About my show schedule and stuff.
What happened? I heard that your shows were getting cancelled.
A fight broke out at one of my most recent shows.
Something stupid about who's more worthy of being my fan.
Pig was there to stop them that time.

I was nothing, really...
*Wink*
Huh? What was that? Do you want something?
Are you looking for praise?
FYI, when it comes to fans bickering and fighting over crap like this,
do you really expect an idol to step in and stop them?

What?!
No, it's not like that!!
Exactly. Because of that, my shows are being cancelled,
and I'm the one who has to take the fall? It doesn't make any sense.
No, it doesn't!
In other words, you did what you were supposed to do.
You merely fulfilled your duty to me,
so don't even think about making those eyes at me again.
Yes, ma'am! I'm sorry, ma'am!
I understand that I was asking for something I didn't deserve!
As long as you get it.
But my show wasn't the only one that was affected...
Some other events saw the same thing happen.
Everyone's been so on edge lately.
Fights have been breaking out at my school too.
I've been seeing that around town too.
I don't know what's going on, but I can't put on any shows right now.
So until this blows over, everything's being put on hold.
Yes, I see...
Fighting, violence and a strange fog that's been covering this city for days.
I'm guessing that's her cue to walk in...
And just who might you be referring to?
Jesus! It actually happened!
Why the surprise? You look like you just saw a ghost.
Hey, y'all there? I'm guessin' Seiran just showed up, which means...
Yes, the Dragon Stream is acting up again.
I'm sure you've all heard about what's been going on lately,
and it has to do with coming in contact with this fog.
It seems that this fog is making it so people want to fight each other.
Right. So this fog's the culprit behind ruining my shows.
Whoever's behind it needs to be punished.
Whoa, Shionyan's eyes are burning with rage...!
Also, Megakin and I did some extra digging,
and discovered that people started disappearing right around the time this fog appeared.
Witnesses are reporting that some kind of monster's lurking within the fog.
A monster...? Then a demon must be behind this.
You got that right. Yo, we got two goals on our hands.
Save the folks that got taken and investigate the Aura Gate.
Aight, Liberators, let's roll out!
